    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/novotel-danang-premier-han-river/hotel/da-nang-vn.html",
    "name": "Novotel Danang Premier Han River",
    "detail": "This was our first trip to Da Nang, and we were unfamiliar with the city and where to stay. Novotel turned out to be a great choice. It was in a great location, an easy walk to many places to eat and activity at night, and to enjoy the sights along the river. The hotel was very comfortable, had a very good breakfast, and a great gym which is important to us and can be a deal breaker when looking for a hotel. The staff were all very pleasant, and always very helpful, particularly with offering ideas for touring the area and arranging day trips for us. We travel frequently in Vietnam, and will certainly choose Novotel again on our next trip to Da Nang. ",
